  "description": "This individual is a compact, broad-shouldered man of middle years with bronze skin and brown eyes set beneath pronounced brow ridges. Brown hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped cut that emphasizes a square jaw and a thickened nose bridge consistent with repeated minor impacts. The hands are notably large and callused, with permanently roughened knuckles and faint healed cuts across the fingers that indicate long familiarity with glass, metal, and hot wash water. A small, pale scar splits the right eyebrow, leaving a slight, enduring asymmetry to the upper face.",
